    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_2805675730857672175.png",
                "key": "洑流劍",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "洑流劍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，若角色未附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">佩伊刻計</span>，則使其附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">佩伊刻計</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">佩伊刻計</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方每抽1張牌後：</span>此牌累積1層<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「壓力階級」</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色使用浮冰增壓時：</span>如果<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「壓力階級」</span>至少有2層，則移除此效果，使技能少花費1元素骰，且如果此技能結算後「壓力階級」至少有4層，則再額外造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/3402e8d6f5344bbe19aaff03729bbdee_8056114720326333478.png",
                "key": "浮冰增壓",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "浮冰增壓"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">潛獵模式</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">潛獵模式</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方抽3張牌後：</span>提供1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span>，保護所附屬角色。（可疊加，最多疊加至2點）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色使用普通攻擊或元素戰技後：</span>將原本元素骰費用最高的至多2張手牌置於牌庫底部，然後抽等量的牌。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：2</span></p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/5689131a4a2251f39d27b6b0a2e5c106_8242878395165191261.png",
                "key": "獵影潛襲",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "獵影潛襲"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害後提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_240059221307810489.png",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span></p><p>此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8178868518031183631.png",
                "key": "規則解釋",
                "materials": [],
